{"tid":1082020,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［工程撚狗入] [JJ插沙] 3份offer揀邊份好，人生大事！！！","createTime":"2019-03-28T16:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T06:08:38.000Z","uid":77762,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9742e64ec52cec572b673e7a30d65226f5486b0d","tid":1082020,"uid":77762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"1）大判開23-24k，6天工作長短週，時間朝8晚6，做平台同大樓，基本13.5糧，14-15個月糧<br />\n<br />\n2）Fitout細公司開23-24k，6天工作，朝9晚6，獨立工作，有2個PC會幫我手，配車配電話，買料一腳踢，公司由落石屎到全科室內裝修都做，感覺上好多野學，做大project多，專項鐵器，防火板，天花。每日都要同鬼頭開會<br />\n<br />\n3）Cutrain wall龍頭大firm開22k，5.5天工作長短，朝9晚6。做玻璃幕牆為主，泥水，佛沙，外牆雲石都會掂，鬼頭公司，全球都有業務。行頭Band 1公司，大Group<br />\n<br />\n1，2基本上等緊我簽名去開工<br />\n3就今日agent幫我叫到價，佢地咁岩公司又要人，未見工<br />\n<br />\n本人hd surveying ，另外讀緊電機hd，本身想投身電個行，點知都係返返轉頭做fitout<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做過2間細firm公司，一間做ABS，一間做site Supervisor <br />\n我就23歲，應該揀大firm好還是揀細公司做返3-5年學夠野轉大公司？/得閒接細job做？<br />\n<br />\n做大判會唔會局限左我將來都係main con都搵食？<br />\n因為就做既野一樣，幢幢樓都咁上下<br />\n但就唔專一範野。<br />\n而我另外擔心係做左大firm，佢專攻玻璃幕牆，我走出去只限死左呢個範圍<br />\n<br />\n自己本身想3年後結婚，所以呢份工應該都影響我將來發展，唔想再行錯路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想真係威返次，同女朋友依家人工差得太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想3年內搵到一筆錢買樓結婚<br />\n<br />\n求各工程界巴打指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ac213f2fa31bd3fa43977bc79ec1321c327643","tid":1082020,"uid":109125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957c26e5641731116521d432239a3d8d1d4864aa","tid":1082020,"uid":77762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f9ac213f2fa31bd3fa43977bc79ec1321c327643","tid":1082020,"uid":109125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:11:33.000Z","msg":"New world有人推薦，協興都有<br />\nFitout就想咩都學識曬，依家自己另外都有接job做<br />\nCurtain wall就得一範，怕香港真係比較小，不過就國際性大group公司，做親都係m+個d"},{"pid":"c5d4caa37d69be9142e91e1d1bac55bb87868d9e","tid":1082020,"uid":121911,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:14:25.000Z","msg":"是但啦 香港地做工程都係做狗 人工最高個份會開心小小"},{"pid":"640da1d9ac054034b7253f0feb89727f28aeee8e","tid":1082020,"uid":77762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5d4caa37d69be9142e91e1d1bac55bb87868d9e","tid":1082020,"uid":121911,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:14:25.000Z","msg":"是但啦 香港地做工程都係做狗 人工最高個份會開心小小"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"巴打我想自己開公司架，唔想只係逗份人工<br />\n想將我做緊學緊既野都會識，唔想是是但但咁做野"},{"pid":"83f77ab25758423fe9fd5d02b99884ce5eb918bb","tid":1082020,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T17:12:53.000Z","msg":"好想3年內搵到一筆錢買樓結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪每個月儲八千蚊，三年後加上爹地果八百萬"},{"pid":"a824000241339fbc60d88c3432ac0cb04896eaaf","tid":1082020,"uid":77762,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"83f77ab25758423fe9fd5d02b99884ce5eb918bb","tid":1082020,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T17:12:53.000Z","msg":"好想3年內搵到一筆錢買樓結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪每個月儲八千蚊，三年後加上爹地果八百萬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T17:13:59.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每個月我都儲緊20k，不過真係飯都食唔飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa76b5b0f8deafee29af0d9ee4a84987bb3add4","tid":1082020,"uid":36437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T17:40:19.000Z","msg":"bms點樣可以轉返去做 bs sub/main con<br />\n做左2年上錯船。。"}